io.github.nucleuspowered.nucleus.api.rtp

Class RTPKernels

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.nucleuspowered.nucleus.api.rtp.RTPKernels

  • public final class RTPKernels
extends Object
    Nucleus supplied RTPKernels.

    A word of warning, if the RTP module has not been initialised, this objects will remain as dummy objects and will not function.

    Check that the NucleusRTPService exists first before attempting to use these kernels.
